		{
			dependencies: ["30B0000000000001"]
			description: [
				"The whole book is one continuous climb. Complete an Age's &lcapstone&r to unlock the next - and the world itself is locked to match:"
				""
				"&2Age I &8Â· &2The Sieve&r - sift the void into metal, forge Sky Steel, automate the forge."
				"&eAge II &8Â· &eThe Kinetic Age&r - Create: water wheels, presses, brass, fan-washing."
				"&2Age III &8Â· &2First Machines&r - kinetics buy electricity. Mekanism opens."
				"&9Age IV &8Â· &9Power & Automation&r - Powah reactors, mob simulation, mechanical sieving. AE2 cracks open mid-tree."
				"&cAge V &8Â· &cWar in the Sky&r - Apotheosis gear, allies, and the &lWither&r."
				"&6Age VI &8Â· &6The Space Program&r - a Nether Star buys your launch codes. Moon to Glacio."
				"&cAge VII &8Â· &cRealms Beyond&r - each planet you conquer unseals a dimension."
				"&5Age VIII &8Â· &5Ascension&r - Twilight fire splits the atom. Antimatter. The Heart."
				""
				"&8Green = done. Blue = available. &lThere is a real ending. Go take it.&r"
				""
				"&7Side quests: &fStash & Sort&7 (drawers, backpacks, search-everything terminals - start this EARLY), &bSky Gadgets&7 (Cyclic conveniences) and &dEssence Farming&7 (Mystical Agriculture - grow diamonds, then nether stars, then godhood). Optional. Recommended. OP.&r"
