		{
			dependencies: ["30B0000000000001"]
			description: [
				"Some advice for staying alive up here:"
				""
				"&a- The void will not kill you.&r Fall off the edge and you are caught before the killing floor, thrown back into the sky above the last solid ground you stood on, and dropped. The landing is free. Your inventory is untouched."
				"&a- Die to anything else and you leave a Gravestone&r where you fell. Break it and everything comes back - armour, hotbar, and your Curios rings too. Right-click it first to read how you died."
				"- Wall off your platform before nightfall - mobs spawn on it."
				"- &cApotheosis&r is live: some mobs carry affixes and become mini-bosses. Rare drops, real danger."
				"- Sleep to skip night until you are strong enough to farm it."
				"- &bPress M&r for the map, &bJ&r for the minimap, &bB&r to drop a waypoint. Xaero's is watching."
				""
				"&8The void is a nuisance now, not an ending. Mobs, bosses and your own ambition are what will actually kill you."
				""
				"Now go build something ridiculous."
			]
